实际上，既然我们说到这个话题，升值，就像你说的，是指东西变得更贵。

133
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,720
something becomes more expensive.
东西变得更贵。

134
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:52,040
The opposite when something becomes cheaper or maybe the value goes down is to depreciate.
相反，当东西变得更便宜或价值下降时，就是贬值。

135
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,400
Depreciate.
贬值。

136
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:56,120
So that D at the beginning means it's going down.
所以开头的D表示下降。

137
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,120
Right.
对。

138
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,120
Okay.
好的。

139
00:05:58,120 --> 00:06:01,240
